Most of the time I cannot tell them apart. I know that’s the point, but they become your life, and that makes them easy to detest. They need directions, commands, guidelines, bullet points, presentations, emails. Not a single original thought. 

<div class="centerAll">All I hear all day is...</div><div class="centerAll container">
